<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11167</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>23585</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西跑进一个空房间。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>23586</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>32306</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>过了一会儿，她变身成为了火箭女孩儿！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>32307</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>38387</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>有时候罗西觉得隐瞒自己的身份很对不起自己的朋友们。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>38388</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>45585</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是罗西决定暂时只把秘密告诉布洛姆市长和潘校长。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>45586</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>49722</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>只有这样她才能够过上普通女孩儿的生活。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>49723</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>53545</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>嗯……其实说普通也并不普通。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>53546</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>57724</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>有多少八岁的孩子需要每天拯救世界呢?</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>57725</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>63865</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>不过现在没有时间想这些了，火箭女孩儿有任务在身！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>63866</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>67642</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西跑过走廊，跑出教学大楼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>67643</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>70110</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好了。”她说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>70111</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>76103</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在我该去看看究竟是什么落在了曼先生的农场里。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>76104</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>79821</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>说完，罗西飞上了天空。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>79822</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>83119</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“快看窗外！” 玛拉大声叫道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>83120</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>89410</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是火箭女孩儿！” 特勒尔说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>89411</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>94431</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很快，罗西就到达了曼先生的农场。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>94432</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>100551</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她看了看周围。有一些玉米杆儿已经被切断。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>100552</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>103681</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然而罗西没有看到宇宙飞船。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>103682</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>107535</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就在这时，玉米地里有什么东西在移动。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>107536</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>113066</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一个人影走向了罗西。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>113067</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>119130</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“天啊！”罗西笑着说，“是个外星人侦探！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>119131</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>124474</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在没空跟你开玩笑。”史密斯侦探皱着眉头说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>124475</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>128877</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>史密斯侦探是美罗城的第一侦探。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>128878</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>133021</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他非常严肃，从来不开玩笑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>133022</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>135722</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好吧。”罗西说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>135723</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>140733</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那么这里究竟发生了什么？宇宙飞船在哪里？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>140734</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>143893</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我也不知道。”史密斯侦探说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>143894</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>148742</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我已经四处找过了。但是哪里也找不到。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>148743</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>153226</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“曼先生看到它飞到哪里了吗？”罗西问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>153227</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>156125</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“没有。”史密斯侦探说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>156126</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>158875</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他太害怕了，马上跑回屋里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>158876</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>161547</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他说自己躲在了床底下。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>161548</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>165503</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>等他重新出来时，宇宙飞船已经不见了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>165504</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>167738</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一些玉米也不见了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>167739</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>172816</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“外星人为什么要拿走玉米呢？”罗西感到诧异。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>172817</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>175020</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她看了看周围。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>175021</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>179075</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她看到一棵折断的大树，就飞了过去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>179076</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>184136</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>‘看上去像是有什么东西撞到了这棵树。’罗西想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>184137</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>187213</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>附近有一个被损坏的围栏。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>187214</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>192995</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西把目光从树移向围栏，然后越过围栏看去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>192996</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>196676</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她看到了一条树木被毁坏的痕迹。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>196677</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>201119</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>‘我猜这一定是宇宙飞船干的。’罗西想，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>201120</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>206423</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>‘但是为什么宇宙飞船没有从这些树的上方飞过？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>206424</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>208387</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>它飞到哪儿去了？’</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>208388</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>212007</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西飞得更高以便看得更清楚。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>212008</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>214959</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那条痕迹通往……</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>214960</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>217182</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西吓了一跳。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>217183</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>230249</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“天啊！我知道宇宙飞船去哪儿了。是美罗城！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>